#IAM SSO MFA Lab

A hands-on Identity & Access Management lab demonstrating **SAML 2.0 SSO** integration with **MFA enforcement** via Conditional Access. Uses **Azure AD / Entra ID** as the IdP and **SimpleSAMLphp** as the test SP. Includes PowerShell automation, config templates, and a validation/audit report generator.

> **Environment:** Azure AD / Entra ID · Okta · SimpleSAMLphp · PowerShell (Microsoft.Graph)  
> **Protocols:** SAML 2.0 · OIDC  
> **Concepts:** SSO · MFA · Conditional Access · Risk-Based Auth · SAML Assertion Inspection

